Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:06.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.17,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this just messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:53.55,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I have to get kicked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.56,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I have more magical power than the royals do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:04.47,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is everything in \Nthis world... isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,This is a load of bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.23,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.28,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.48,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:28.75,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'll show the Clover Kingdom's \NMagic Knights the true extent of my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:48.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:53.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:57.86,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:02.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.04,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.04,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:17.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:24.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:29.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:35.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:42.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:45.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:49.50,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.69,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Capital Riot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to run from these jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:15.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calling us peasants, rats, \Nembarrassments, failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you think we're worthy or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'm going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.40,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.24,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't even be allowed to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.27,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.76,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pile up merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and shut you all up!
