Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.35,sign_5676_49_Sol,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sol
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.35,sign_5676_50_Charlotte,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte
