Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.86,sign_5760_52_Alecdora,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Alecdora
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.86,sign_5760_53_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:03.36,sign_5844_54_Solid,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Solid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:03.36,sign_5844_55_Nozel,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:03.36,sign_5760_53_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nebra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.80,sign_5928_57_You_fool_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,You fool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.37,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Become...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.25,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,...the Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.34,main,Solid and Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.39,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Binding Magic: Sea Serpent's Coils!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.73,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:43.90,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Binding Magic: Mist Spider's Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.11,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.84,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He's erasing the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.59,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He's no ordinary peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:06.95,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.09,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,If that's his attack range, \Nthere's no reason for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.89,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: Sand-Armored Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.78,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.45,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:39.74,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,To act in such a way at a festive occasion\Nlike the decoration ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.46,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,You will surely be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.15,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.97,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Why so soft, Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:56.27,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone that self-confident \Nneeds to be taught a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.06,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,So that they can never talk back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.78,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Water Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.83,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.86,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just make me kneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.86,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly peasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.32,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not holding back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, p-please, no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.56,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:26.31,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, don't be so quick to use \Nyour magic on a mere peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.61,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.01,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.07,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to shame the Silva family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.19,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this chill in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:41.97,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cold pressure that's \Ndifferent from Captain Yami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:47.11,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Captain of the Silver Eagles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:51.77,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,A peasant that foolishly tried to\Ndefy royalty... How shall I punish you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:01.31,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?\NAt this rate, Asta will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.65,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting so worked \Nup over a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.95,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed of yourself, Silvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.00,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Mimosa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.67,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:37.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,All right, rejoice! I, Leopold Vermillion,\Ndeclare you my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:40.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.23,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name? Casta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold, it's Asta. He's Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.67,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, eh? That's a great name, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.32,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now! Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.86,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:09.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold and Fuegoleon are my cousins.
