Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:20.26,sign_13261_120_Fuegoleon_s_Moth,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon's\N{\fs14}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:20.26,sign_13261_121_Fuegoleon_s_Fath,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon's\N{\fs14}Father
