Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:15.34,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,My father's older brother is \NFuegoleon and Leopold's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:20.26,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Also, my mother's older \Nsister is Noelle's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.63,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Too many royals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.51,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:29.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thanks, but my rival's actually \NYuno, who's standing over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:35.37,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! One can never \Nhave too many rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:41.08,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta! You have a very nice body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.41,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed qualified to be my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.76,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let us arm wrestle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.15,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Guys really are dumb, aren't they, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.42,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your manners, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.14,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.44,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain," Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.44,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.76,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Sol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.80,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.51,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.03,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is now really the time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.22,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding back? Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:15.52,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming Leopold's rival...\NAsta truly is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:21.24,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,My, aren't we all so very noisy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.87,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:29.37,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,A royal acknowledging a peasant as his rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:40.48,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Julius allowed the boy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:44.78,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a peasant, but doesn't \Nhe deserve a little credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:49.73,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd hear such \Nnonsense from a royal's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.95,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the Vermillion \Nfamily has gone soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.52,main,Noze,0000,0000,0000,,You're a disgrace to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.15,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.40,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,How am I, an eagle that soars the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.41,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,supposed to give any credit to an \Ninsect that crawls on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:19.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a tremendous clash of mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Holy crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't feel their mana,\NI can tell... that this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.71,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we stop them, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.09,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,This is foolish. Ignore the men \Nand their boorish fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.75,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Also, call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.74,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.44,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.67,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.46,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.81,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,The capital is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.01,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.90,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy, destroy, destroy, destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.69,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.60,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy all the fools who \Ncan't understand my worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:30.30,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Such disgusting creatures. \NWhere did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.35,main,Minion B,0000,0000,0000,,You must not value your lives, if you're\Ninvading the royal capital like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.41,main,Minion C,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.23,main,Minion B,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming toward us even \Nwhen we shoot their limbs off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.49,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Do not falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.15,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Clover Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.66,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to, you scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:55.70,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, scum! Scum! Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.25,italics,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.20,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than me, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.47,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.67,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Capital is under attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:44.52,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Creation Magic: \NStone Model of the World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a three-dimensional \Nmodel of the Noble Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Even the voices of the people at \Nthe scene and their magic levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:15.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Is he lacing the whole area with mana \Nand simultaneously making it visible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:19.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more advanced than \Nmy Magic Flower Guidepost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.36,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,A force with this much magic appears \Nin five places simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.57,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,without us noticing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:30.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,A formidable spatial magic user must have \Nmade them materialize in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:35.22,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, the guard mages of \Nthe Noble Realm work in shifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.35,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,constantly keeping a magic barrier in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.56,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It should be impossible to \Nenter with spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.53,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Did they analyze the barrier's \Nmechanism and break through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:48.27,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Or did one of the guard mages betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.86,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they must \Nbe phenomenally skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.36,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,How should we assign the \Nmembers we currently have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.62,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to guard the \Narea around the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what the heck are we waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! There are people \Nout there who need our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you plan to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:13.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the full situation yet, \Nand you can't sense magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:18.30,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.55,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.83,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.55,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Asta, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.87,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Guys really are dumb, aren't they, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.17,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.52,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,And call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.68,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Leo's still very much a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.20,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to thoroughly retrain him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:45.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd rather not take orders \Nfrom me, but listen well, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.85,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after Leo and that Black Bulls boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.96,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,and after I've joined them,\Nwe'll head to the north district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.92,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You, Black Bulls girl, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.08,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Eagles, I ask that you \Nhead to the central district,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.50,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,where the magic is strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.49,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Roses, head to the east district!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.12,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not take orders from a man, \Nbut I suppose I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.08,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:16.19,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Dawn, split into two teams and head \Nto the west and northwest districts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.53,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect the people of the Nobel Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.90,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.79,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have \Nto save dessert for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.27,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail to protect the royal capital, \Nwe'll bring shame upon the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.04,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let the enemy escape, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.59,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:40.04,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.96,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get in by following \NAsta and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like something \Nawful is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.47,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a job for Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:59.68,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,If I do good, I might get the chance \Nto eat even better food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.33,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I smell something delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:08.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fuel up before the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.67,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.73,main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're going to get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.09,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.05,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.69,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East District
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.92,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your manners, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:47.16,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:54.98,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:05.07,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Those who dare to bring chaos upon the \Nkingdom shall perish before my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:36.38,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These things keep getting \Nup with half-assed attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.09,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:48.37,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}West District
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.96,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should work off \Nsome calories before dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:59.52,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Fools who disturb the peace of the capital...\NYou shall be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:05.05,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sigh,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1, 1037)}North District
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:18.68,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen them before. \NWhat country is that army from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:35.48,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl... Do you like the Clover Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:38.08,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:43.19,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.49,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:52.12,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,So the town... the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.54,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:44.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:49.80,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:55.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:22:00.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:02.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:05.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:08.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:16.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:19.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:21.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:26.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:30.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:36.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:40.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:55.49,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.45,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:59.00,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Mr. Animal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,An animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Woof, woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:13.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A dog... My, how adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But a cat might be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.49,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:25.15,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but maybe something \Neven wilder, like a wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:27.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All men are wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.95,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just can't choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.79,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:39.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What a creepy enemy! But there's \Nno time to be creeped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:43.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect the citizens \Nof the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:46.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 22:\N"Wild Magic Dance."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:51.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 22\N\N{\fs18} Wild Magic Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:49.88,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt, please come to me!
